<item>
            <title>[OAK-2356] Logic for writing properties in SegmentWriter.writeNode looks off</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-2356</link>
                <project id="12313221" key="OAK">Jackrabbit Oak</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-2192?focusedCommentId=14245381&amp;amp;page=com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.issuetabpanels:comment-tabpanel#comment-14245381&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;mentioned &lt;/a&gt; by &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=alex.parvulescu&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;alex.parvulescu&quot;&gt;alex.parvulescu&lt;/a&gt;, the condition at line 1096 of &lt;tt&gt;SegmentWriter&lt;/tt&gt; looks off: &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;} &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (!(before &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;instanceof&lt;/span&gt; SegmentNodeState) || store.containsSegment(before.getRecordId().getSegmentId())) {
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In fact it looks like a refactoring accident introduced with &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-631&quot; title=&quot;SegmentMK: Implement garbage collection&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;OAK-631&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;OAK-631&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;- || ((SegmentNodeState) before).getStore() != store) {
+ || store.containsSegment(((SegmentNodeState)before)
        .getRecordId().getSegmentId())) {
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;where the negation has just been forgotten. See &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/jackrabbit-oak/commit/d96eb8c3ea8738695780b6a03c4902f0ce1f337f#diff-cd2b669b9d707784b58ff1783748f932&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/jackrabbit-oak/commit/d96eb8c3ea8738695780b6a03c4902f0ce1f337f#diff-cd2b669b9d707784b58ff1783748f932&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
